data.name: changeGameInstallDirectoryToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Point KKManager to a different game install.

data.name: installANewModToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Attempt to install a plugin or a zipmod. For plugins, patchers and especially non-zipmod mods it's recommended to follow the installation steps provided by the author instead.

data.name: openIndividualDownloadWebsiteToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: You can download zipmods individually here instead of updating the whole modpack.

data.name: checkForUpdatesOnStartupToolStripMenuItem.Text
data.value: Check for mod updates on startup

data.name: checkForUpdatesOnStartupToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: The Mod updater menu button will turn green if there is an update available.

data.name: useSystemProxyServerToolStripMenuItem.Text
data.value: Use system proxy server for FTP (needs restart)

data.name: p2PDownloaderSettingsToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Note: FTP connections are still required even with P2P enabled.

data.name: fixFileAndFolderPermissionsToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: This will attempt to fix any file or folder permission issues in the game directory. Make sure that no other applications are using anything inside the game directory before uisng, otherwise a PC restart might be required to be able to access some of the files again.

data.name: compressGameFilesToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Reduce the size of the game by recompressing its asset bundles with a higher compression level. Generally safe but might cause issues in rare cases, especially with newer games like RG or HC. If in doubt, back up the abdata and *_Data folders.

data.name: cleanUpDuplicateZipmodsToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Attempt to automatically clean up zipmods with the same GUIDs so that only the latest versions are left.

data.name: cleanUpDuplicateAndInvalidZipmodsToolStripMenuItem.Text
data.value: Clean up duplicate and invalid zipmods...

data.name: languagesToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: To fully change the language KKManager needs to be restarted.

data.name: tryToDeleteToRecycleBinToolStripMenuItem.Text
data.value: Try to delete to Recycle Bin

data.name: tryToDeleteToRecycleBinToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Attempt to move files to the recycle bin when deleting cards/mods/plugins and when updating mods. If this fails for whatever reason (e.g. recycle bin is full or disabled) the files are deleted permanently.
